   "source": [
    "# Some important facts\n",
    "\n",
    "There are a few important facts in the ACCESS-NRI Intake catalog that users should be aware of."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. The catalog returns `Datasets` (not `Dataarray`s)\n",
    "\n",
    "This is because with the catalog you can load multiple variables into a single dataset with a single call (when these variables are in the same file). For example,"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data_ic_multivar = catalog[experiment].search(\n",
    "    variable=[\"surface_salt\", \"surface_temp\"], \n",
    "    frequency=\"1mon\"\n",
    ").to_dask()"
   ]
  },
